    Scope and Contents
Illinois' delegate to the 1976 Democratic National Convention and member of the Platform Committee. 
Platform Committee hearing testimony, correspondence from witnesses, constituents and presidential candidates, and drafts  and final copies of the 1976 Democratic Platform.  Includes letters from constituents urging support of Common Cause "Making  Government Work" plank; and urging reversal of the decision to oppose a Constitutional  Amendment to prohibit abortion.  
  
